tweet: DID YOU KNOW: The Emilia Romagna GP is the third different name used for an F1 world championship event at @autodromoimola.  The circuit made its F1 debut in 1980 as host of the Italian GP before hosting the San Marino GP between 1981-2006.  🎥 x @F1  #ExperienceF1 #ImolaGP 🇮🇹
